  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate Efficacy and Safety of Zolpidem Modified Release Formulation in Insomnia Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Open-Label, Active-Controlled, Parallel-Group Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Zolpidem Modified Release (MR) in Patients With Primary Insomnia</official_title>
  <sponsors>
