  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to investigate the efficacy and safety of zolpidem modified
      release (MR) tablet using estazolam (Eurodin) as a comparative drug in patients with primary
      insomnia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
